metadataAttributes.Title: High Performance Collaboration: Leadership, Teamwork, and Negotiation
metadataAttributes.Short Intro: Are leaders born or made?  Learn the essential skills to develop and expand your leadership repertoire,  design teams for collaboration, and craft win-win negotiation strategies. High Performance Collaboration: Leadership, Teamwork, and Negotiation focuses on leadership, teamwork, and negotiation. Students will engage in self-assessments to analyze their leadership style, develop team charters to optimize their groups, and develop a game plan for effective negotiation.
